text: int main ( ) { int n , a , b , i , gcd , min , lcm ; scanf ( "%d" , & n ) ; while ( n -- ) { scanf ( "%d %d" , & a , & b ) ; min = a > b ? a : b ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= min ; i ++ ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) { gcd = i ; } } lcm = a * b / gcd ; printf ( "%d %d\n" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
